<plot>When Peter Parker is given a plum job with a research complex with the help of Wilson Fisk, it seems to be a dream come true. However, that dream soon turns into a nightmare when he is accused of treason. Even when he assigned a top lawyer in the name of Matt Murdock, his situation seems hopeless. Regardless, Parker is determined to clear his name and his fight is joined by Murdock who secretly helps him as the blind superhero, Daredevil. Together, this pair must face the long odds as they battle the true traitors who set Parker up.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?510282</url></doc>
